body.description: For generations, Disney Princess characters have brought children tales of courage and integrity, generosity and kindness. Hasbro celebrates this timeless legacy with a wide range of fashion and small dolls featuring movie-inspired details and fun accessories that lets little ones recreate favorite adventures or imagine their own new stories. With so many beloved characters to choose from -- Ariel, Aurora, Belle, Cinderella, Jasmine, Merida, Moana, Mulan, Pocahontas, Rapunzel, Snow White, and Tiana--there's a Disney Princess for everyone! manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Characters from Disney Zombies 3 Worlds collide in Disney Zombies 3, and the town of Seabrook will never be the same! Get to know movie characters Addison, Zed, Willa, and A-spen with this fashion doll collection. Pretend these long-time Seabrook residents and out of this world visitors are discovering that being different is what makes you special!

Poseable 12-Inch Fashion Dolls Imagine scenes from the Disney Zombies 3 movie! Dolls are 12 inches tall with articulated joints. They have 11 points of articulation including shoulders, hips, knees, elbows, wrists, and head. Pose the figures out in character-inspired stances to imagine creating scenes from the film. Iconic Movie Outfits and Accessories Each doll comes with one outfit, a pair of shoes, and accessories inspired by their looks in the movie. Outfits and accessories are removable for fun dress-up play. Look for other Disney Zombies 3 figures to swap styles. Fashions are inspired by each characters' Seabrook faction -- alien, werewolf, and Zombie! Inspired by the Hit Disney Franchise Start a collection of fashion dolls inspired by the third installment of the hit Disney Zombies franchise! Dolls are great for fans of the movies and kids ages 6 and up. Dolls are inspired by specific scenes and styles within the movie. They come with iconic, story-inspired accessories including Zed's Z-Band, Willa's Moonstone necklace, and A-spen and Addison's Luma Lens bracelets.
